<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Here are excerpts from the statement from the <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> ethics committee which accompanied its statement of alleged violations by <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> Speaker <PERSON> Jim </PERSON> <PERSON> Wright </PERSON>. These excerpts focus on those matters where the committee did not `` find reason to believe'' <PERSON> Wright </PERSON> had violated <ORGANIZATION> House </ORGANIZATION> rules and on the one matter the committee is still pursuing.
