<FIRST>a a BC-History Adv23   04-17 0456</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-History, Adv23,0474</SECOND>
<HEAD>$adv23</HEAD>
<HEAD>For Release Sunday, April 23</HEAD>
<HEAD>Today In History</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
