injured when part of the roof of an <ORGANIZATION> Aloha </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Airlines </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Boeing </ORGANIZATION> 737 peeled back during a flight from <LOCATION> Hilo </LOCATION> to <LOCATION> Honolulu </LOCATION>. Today's birthdays: Syndicated columnist <PERSON> Rowland </PERSON> <PERSON> Evans </PERSON> is 68. Actress-singer <PERSON> Ann-Margret </PERSON> is 48. Actress <PERSON> Marcia </PERSON> <PERSON> Strassman </PERSON> is 41. Thought for today: `` Anger would break the whole world to pieces if it could.'' _ <PERSON> Frederick </PERSON> <PERSON> William </PERSON> <PERSON> Faber </PERSON>, English theologian, 1814-1863.
